Either I'm going to explode or I've found a revolutionary formula that will solve our nation's fuel problems.

THIS is the best fucking soup I've ever eaten.

Ah, might as well put in a serious entry here.

I'll tell you about how Wednesday went at school.

Last time I checked, my grade in Chemistry class is 26%.  This is due to falling asleep as soon as I sit down at my desk and waking up only to go to my next class.  My mother was kind of upset and said I had to pull up my grade in there.  I had missed school on Monday and I didn't go to Chemistry on Tuesday so I had take a make-up test on Wednesday.  Of course I knew nothing about Chemistry so I was in a dilemma.  The rest of the class was moving on to cover new things so the teacher asked if I wanted to go to the library to take my test where I could concentrate.  I said yes and immediately went to the biology class down the hall where most people were familiar with Chemistry.  Thanks to their help, I completed the test.  I then left the "library" and came back to Chemistry where I turned in my test, made fun of the foreign exchange student and tried to fall asleep.
